1 contained in Sections 2, 3, and 4 of this Act to the county clerk of each county, and the
2 county clerk shall have the entirety of the question and the amendment, as so certified,
3 indicated on the ballots provided to the voters in paper or electronic form as applicable to
4 the voting machines in use in each county or precinct.
